# Absolute(0) Stability Framework (ASV3)

A real-time invariant-governed stability engine for dynamic systems.

ASV3 enforces bounded, safe system evolution under arbitrary inputs using:
- Projection-based constraint enforcement
- Lyapunov-style energy control
- Adaptive budget tightening
- Multi-layer coherence metrics (TSC)

## Key Result
Across 200-step multi-domain simulations:
- 0 invariant violations
- 100% bounded trajectories
- Stable under adversarial and chaotic inputs

